	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you have all the pieces, you need Qeynos faction of warmly to do the turn in. <br><br>Faction to do the quest can be obtained in under 2 hours by giving two gold pieces to a cleric npc in Qeynos. Lashun Novashine I believe, if I remember correctly. Hail him, then give him two gold pieces at a time. Just keep doing the hail and gold, until he cons warmly. It all depends what your faction is at the time on how long it will take. It's boring, but very affective. As a side trip, you could kill Putrid Skeletons at the South Karana undead camp, just be careful if the Aegis of Ro quest npc's spawn.<br><br>Sincerely,<br>The Vinman<br>&nbsp;<br>For the Good of the Realms!</td></tr>
