	   <tr><td colspan=2>As far as I've ever been able to find, it is NOT rechargable.&nbsp;&nbsp;I know there's at least one or two people on Innoruuk that have done the entire SF quest more than once just for the charges of healing.  Once they're gone, they're gone.  <br><br>Regarding how many people ~ it totally depends.  I watched a guild group of about 15 people die horribly one day because when they pulled Sir Lucan, they got every single militia guard as well.  I *think* that group was in their 40s but not totally sure.  When I did my SF, I had a level 60 monk and a level 60 ranger help me and it was fine.  Did need to use LH on the monk but otherwise everything went fine.  Both of those level 60s were in the uber-guild on the server at the time and had literally the best gear available in the game... and they knew how to pull and get only Lucan and his pet cleric.  <br><br>Good luck!<br>&nbsp;<br>Danaelle Bladesong ~ Lord Protector of Quellious<br>Danaere Passionheart ~ Druid of Tunare<br>Ashen Vendetta ~ Innoruuk Server</td></tr>
